To create exe from 'egp_scribe.py':
    1) install pyinstaller -> from command line, run the following:
        pip3 install pyinstaller
        then close command line
    2) open command line terminal from folder where you've saved 'egp_scribe.py'
    3) run the following
        pyinstaller -F egp_scribe.py
    
    When process is complete, exe will be located in dist folder. 

*exe is not included in this GitHub repo strictly because of file size limitations
